ReportBundle.ReportXML: <Report ReportGID="d38642b7-f620-417d-9516-ff1329d394b9" ReportUseType="2" ReportType="5" ReportName="Load Accuracy Graph" CreatedDT="2014-05-16T14:47:59.297" ModifiedDT="2014-05-22T16:55:33.857" ModifiedBy="VAS" ConcurrencyTS="AAAAAAAAoWQ=" ReportVersion="0" />

ReportQuery.ReportQueryText: <QueryBundle> <QueryText>select * from ( select fs.InstanceDate as ReportDate, LoadAvgErrorPct = avg(case when it2.TargetUnitQuantity = 0 then 0 else 100 * ABS(it2.TargetUnitQuantity - it2.UnitQuantity) / it2.TargetUnitQuantity end), DropAvgErrorPct = avg(case when it1.TargetUnitQuantity = 0 then 0 else 100 * ABS(it1.TargetUnitQuantity - it1.UnitQuantity) / it1.TargetUnitQuantity end), l.LocationName as Pen, u.UserID as [User], e.LocationName as Equipment, ii.InventoryItemName as Ingredient, pt.PenTypeName as PenType from FeedingSchedule fs join FeedingScheduleMix fsm on fsm.FeedingScheduleGID = fs.FeedingScheduleGID join FeedingScheduleLoad fsl on fsl.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID join FeedingScheduleDrop fsd on fsd.FeedingScheduleLoadGID = fsl.FeedingScheduleLoadGID join InventoryTransaction it1 on it1.TransactionSourceGID = fsd.FeedingScheduleDropGID join FeedingScheduleMixInstruction fsmi on fsmi.FeedingScheduleMixGID = fsm.FeedingScheduleMixGID and fsmi.InventoryItemGID = it1.InventoryItemGID join InventoryTransaction it2 on it2.TransactionSourceGID = fsmi.FeedingScheduleMixInstructionGID join InventoryItem ii on ii.InventoryItemGID = it2.InventoryItemGID join Location l on l.LocationGID = fsd.LocationGID join Pen p on p.LocationGID = l.LocationGID join [User] u on u.UserGID = fsd.ByUserGID join Location e on e.LocationGID = it2.ToLocationGID outer apply(select top 1 PenTypeName from PenType pt join PenPenType ppt on ppt.PenTypeGID = pt.PenTypeGID where ppt.PenGID = p.PenGID and ppt.IsPrimary = 1) pt group by fs.InstanceDate, l.LocationName, u.UserID, e.LocationName, pt.PenTypeName, ii.InventoryItemName) z where 1=1</QueryText> <PreQueryText /> </QueryBundle>
